Class ManagedObjectReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.inventory.ManagedObjectReference

  • public class ManagedObjectReference
extends Object
    ManagedObjectReference is the container to place references in ManagedObjects.

    Could be used in this reference collections:

    • childAssets
    • childDevices
    • parentAssets
    • parentDevices

    Created by Patrick Steinert on 03.09.16.
